HELP . /help = Shows this message.
HELP . /help 'command name' = Shows more info about the command.

BASH . /bash 'command' = Run normal commands in Raspberry Pi and show the output.

MATH . /math 'equation' = Solves common math equations.

WIKI . /wiki (en, fi, ru etc.) 'search' = Search from wikipedia. Gives you text
WIKI . /lwiki (en, fi, ru etc.) 'search' = Search from wikipedia. Gives you link

TIME . /time = Tells current time according to the server.

JOKE . /joke = Tells random joke.
JOKE . /joke 'name' = Tells joke called 'name'.
JOKE . /joke list = Shows all available joke names.
JOKE . /joke 'name' 'your joke' = Saves new joke called 'name'.

HI . /hi = Bot greets the user and tells how he is feeling currently. 

FD . /fd = Shows what flagday is currently if any.
FD . /fd 'date' = Shows what flagday is at given date if any.

WEATHER . /weather = show today's weather
WEATHER . /weather all = show todays and next five days weather
WEATHER . /weather sun = shows today's sunrise and sunset 

TRANSLATE . /translate ( en, fi, ru etc. ) ( en, fi, ru etc. ) sentence\ne.g. /translate ru how are you
TRANSLATE . /translate = Show all languages.

LOG . /log (f) = Shows chat log. 'f' = full.

QUIZ . /quiz (rounds) (players at start) = Starts the quiz. 
QUIZ . More players may join at any time.
QUIZ . Say 'stop' to stop game while running.

MC . Works only with permission:
MC . /mc start = starts the server.
MC . /mc 'server command'
